          Our mission is to execute exemplary, life-affirming live theatre.<br>
          We promise we’re not haughty; we’re named after a spaceship from a science fiction novel.<br>
        </p><p class="lead">
          Like the Greeks, we believe that theatre should be for everyone.<br>
          Like a former Chicago mayor, we believe that politicians don’t bring people together. Artists do. <br>
          And like that famous Spanish painter, we believe that art is the lie that tells the truth. <br>
        </p><p class="lead">
          All in all, we think that theatre is the finest living exhibition of the human spirit. <br>
